            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Slice the <strong>cherry</strong>&nbsp;<strong>tomatoes</strong> in half&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Place them cut-side up onto a baking tray,&nbsp;drizzle<span class=\"text-highlight\"> with <strong>olive oil</strong> and</span> a pinch of&nbsp;<strong>sugar&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n<p>Put the tray in the oven and bake for 20-25 min or until the tomatoes are starting to blister</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
