    {
      "instruction": "<p>Peel and thinly slice the <strong>shallot<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong></p>\r\n<p>Peel and finely chop (or grate) the <strong>garlic&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n<p>Combine the <strong>chopped&nbsp;</strong><strong>garlic</strong>, <strong>sliced&nbsp;</strong><strong>shallot</strong>, <strong>ground&nbsp;</strong><strong>cumin</strong>, <strong>mango chutney</strong>, 2 tbsp <span class=\"text-danger\">[4 tbsp]</span> <strong>olive oil</strong> and 1 tbsp <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tbsp]</span> <strong>water</strong></p>\r\n<p>Season with <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>peppe</strong>r <span class=\"text-highlight\">&ndash;</span> this is your <strong>dressing</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
